The '''crimson-rumped myzomela''' ('''''Myzomela eichhorni''''') or '''yellow-vented myzomela''', is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Meliphagidae]].
It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to the [[Western Province (Solomon Islands)]].

